longBusinessSummary: NuVista Energy Ltd., an oil and natural gas company, engages in the exploration, development, and production of oil and natural gas reserves in the Western Canadian Sedimentary Basin. It primarily focuses on the condensate rich Montney formation in the Wapiti and Pipestone areas of the Alberta Deep Basin. NuVista Energy Ltd. was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
